   2. In (the film) ``Aradhana (Prayer),'' which vehicle is Rajesh
Khanna traveling in while singing the song ``Mere sapno ki rani kab
(Queen of my dreams, when will you come to me?)''?
</P>
<P>
   A. Autorickshaw
</P>
<P>
   B. Jeep
</P>
<P>
   C. Cycle
</P>
