</P>
<P>
   South Africa
</P>
<P>
   TITLE: Who Wants to Be a Millionaire
</P>
<P>
   TOP PRIZE: 1 million rand ($144,600)  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   HOST: Jeremy Maggs, news anchor and morning show host
</P>
<P>
   1. Which word do fans commonly use when a South African soccer
team scores a goal?
</P>
<P>
   A. Ayta!
</P>
<P>
   B. Ahyay!
</P>
<P>
