   COSTARICA-INVEST _ SAN JOSE, Costa Rica _ Lured by cheap land, a
gorgeous countryside and pleasant climate, thousands of U.S.
citizens have moved to Costa Rica in recent years. Profile some of
these folks, from retirees to surfers. Have they found the dream
they wanted? Do locals accept them? Has the recent upswing in crime
tainted their tropical paradise? (Williams, Cox News Service) WITH
