<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Don't be fooled; nobody follows Bible to the letter
 &HT;    By Steve Gushee
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Sen. Joseph Lieberman chooses which
biblical laws to follow literally and which he will modify to suit
his needs.
</P>
<P>
   Most religious conservatives condemn that approach. But Jesus
