Journal-Constitution) 25.
</P>
<P>
   FOOTBALL/COLLEGES
</P>
<P>
   FBC-TEXAS-PREVIEW _The Road to the Orange Bowl: Texas.
(Barnhart, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 25.
</P>
